{"tid":1740410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界即刻周圍貼二噁英禍害既文宣","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T04:08:55.000Z","uid":147367,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18dda9e00bfe0766f9a99fc83ae5eeedf67c7c05","tid":1740410,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"藍屍都係自私既，你講點樣殺人佢都無感覺<br />\n但係當佢知道二噁英會害到佢無孫抱佢就會驚到仆街"},{"pid":"962ea2a0f031d41a79e8f42e5b0cafba81dfd8c2","tid":1740410,"uid":21095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0253d4d24476fa12e2c0d1d8cbd063a6285a7786","tid":1740410,"uid":188393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"文宣要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96b0ffe3212bce950ecc9d7e82bd28ccee8c741","tid":1740410,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1fad1ba46d564c863171d952ab903a7c99d718","tid":1740410,"uid":264891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgfSH1k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgfSH1k.png&h=531b7e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7RRYzG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7RRYzG.png&h=ff858d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dBB9Go.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dBB9Go.png&h=5dd01e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ReW9GO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ReW9GO.png&h=cc533191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Opegqe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpegqe9.png&h=d91979fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5uTstw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5uTstw.png&h=a5639f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人讀化學出生所以知道dioxin到底有幾可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塞維索事件為發生於1976年7月10日12時37分的工業事故，位於意大利倫巴第大區米蘭北方約20公里的小型化學工廠，為史上最嚴重的2,3,7,8-四氯雙苯-p-戴奧辛（TCDD）污染事件<br />\n<br />\n1976年時，塞維索一家化學工廠的三氯酚反應器因為冷卻水不足，使外側的蒸汽渦輪將反應器的升溫至攝氏300度，導致反應失控，大量戴奧辛及其他有毒物洩出。附近土地受到嚴重污染，隨後有大量動物死亡，居民也陸續發生各種病變，即為塞維索事件。<br />\n<br />\n該事件促進了相關科學研究及工業安全規範的制定，歐洲聯盟的工業安全法規又被稱作塞維索II指令（英語：Directive 96/82/EC）。"},{"pid":"d15f041918ec77336bf546b4d67331ae10669f8e","tid":1740410,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"[死線文宣] 直擊要害 - 請手動轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1740571\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1740571</a><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">走日本仔</span></span></strong>時驚唔驚？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大批鬥</span></span></strong>驚唔驚？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">紅衞兵</span></span></strong>驚唔驚？<br />\n<br />\n依家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">共产党</span></span></strong>又打到來啦<br />\n會共晒你的錢，仲敢唔敢收佢地的蛇齋餅粽？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGWiDxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGWiDxi.gif&h=e2aa19f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好人一世平安"}]}